Gains a permanent +2 to his maximum FP.


Standing Stone Ability: Infiltrator's Edge
Unmatched Talent: His innate genius manifests as uncanny luck. He may re-roll any single failed Lockpicking or Trap Disarming attempt once per dungeon.
Secret Passage: Once per adventure, he may declare that he has found a "secret passage," allowing the party to bypass one non-boss encounter or puzzle entirely.


The Con Artist's Gambit:
Once per social encounter, Caelan can ask the GM to reveal the primary motivation (e.g., Greed, Fear, Pride) of the NPC he is talking to, giving him a massive advantage in any subsequent negotiation.



